                    "name": "Submersible",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "text": "The apparatus of the octopus can protect its crew and passengers from water pressure to a maximum depth of 5,000 feet and contains enough air for 12 hours for a pilot alone or 6 hours for a pilot and passenger or crew member."
